# Use Case - Monitoring Web

Workflow n8n pour monitoring web automatis√©: navigation automatique, screenshots, alertes Slack si erreur. Adaptation du workflow monitoring-web du repo ai-automation-stack.

```json
{
  "nodes": [
    {"type": "cron", "parameters": {"interval": "15m"}},
    {"type": "web-navigation"},
    {"type": "screenshot"},
    {"type": "slack", "parameters": {"alert": true}}
  ],
  "connections": [[0,1],[1,2],[2,3]],
  "description": "Automated web monitoring with screenshots and Slack alerts every 15min."
}
```
